  "description": "snap_decay at maximum (8s) dissolves the percussive identity entirely. pitchLock off, heavy unison, SCHOOL macro high — the neon tetra school shimmers in suspension. What starts as a struck bell becomes a metallic drone that breathes across the stereo field. The snap trigger is a distant memory by the time the tone fully blooms.",
